    {q:`The gross GST liability (before reduction of ITC) for the month of January is`,opts:[`' 76,500 CGST and ' 76,500 SGST`,`' 89,100 CGST and ' 89,100 SGST`,`' 1,02,600 CGST and ' 1,02,600 SGST`,`' 1,52,100 CGST and ' 1,52,100 SGST`],ans:0,exp:`' 76,500 CGST and ' 76,500 SGST. Total value of taxable supply – Particulars Amount (') Maintenance charges for 100 4BHK flats (' 8,500 × 100) 8,50,000 [' 10,000 – ' 1,500 property tax (taxes collected on behalf of municipal corporation are exempted from GST)]. [Since value of maintenance per month is more than ' 7,500 per member it is not exempted]. Maintenance charges for 20 shops (' 7,000 × 20). - [The exemption of ' 7,500 of maintenance per month is also available to shops as it is the member of Society]. Total value of taxable supply. 8,50,000 Total GST liability = ' 76,500 [(' 8,50,000 ×`}
